\id JON
\h Yunus
\toc1 Yunus
\toc2 Yunus
\toc3 Yun.
\mt1 Yunus
\c 1
\s1 Tarewřa n Yunus
\m 
\v 1 Awař n SIDI yusa-dd ɣar Yunus, mmis n Amittay, inna:
\v 2 “Kkar, ruḥ ɣar tendint n Ninwa tameqqrant uca barreḥ ḍidd nnes minzi tuɛeffna nsen tgeɛɛed \add am ict n arriḥet yarṣuden\add* ař udem inu.” \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Amz. 10:11, 12; Yun. 3:3\x*
\v 3 \add Maca\add* Yunus ikkar ḥima ad yarweř zeg wudem n SIDI. Netta ihwa ɣar \add tendint n\add* Yafa uca yufa \add din\add* ict n tɣarrabut ad traḥ ɣar \add tendint n\add* Tarcic. Netta ixeǧeṣ ttaman \add n usafar\add* uca inya dayes maḥend ad iraḥ ɣar Tarcic, ixs ad iggʷej x wudem n SIDI.
\v 4 \add Maca\add* SIDI issekk-dd asemmiḍ ijhed x řebḥar uca yarni idweř d taḥaryaḍt tameqqrant x řebḥar ařami ɛřaḥař tiweḍ ad tarẓ tɣarrabut.
\v 5 Ggʷeden ibeḥriyyen uca kuř aryaz isɣuy, ittar ɣar arebbi nnes uca nḍaren řeqcuɛ nni di tɣarrabut ɣar řebḥar ḥima ad xas ssneqṣen ddqeř. Tuɣa ihwa-dd Yunus maca ɣar uɣezdis aḍeffar n tɣarrabut, izzeř din uca iṭṭeṣ ijj n yiḍeṣ yuǧeɣ.
\v 6 Yusa-dd ɣares bab n tɣarrabut, inna as: “Min tᵉttegged, mayemmi dinni tᵉṭṭṣed? Kkar, řaɣa x AREBBI nnec, ad taɣ AREBBI nnec ad aneɣ ifekkar ḥima war nɣarreq ca.”
\v 7 Nnan yeryazen i wayawya: “As-dd, ejj aneɣ ad nḍar taqedduḥt, ḥima ad nessen wi d aneɣ iggin di nnɛi-ya.” Nitni nḍaren taqedduḥt uca tusa-dd tqedduḥt deg Yunus.
\m 
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* nnan as: “Ini aneɣ, mayemmi d aneɣ teḥkem nnɛi-ya. Min teɛna řxedmet nnec? Manis dd-tusid? Min teɛna tammurt nnec u zi man řgens i ɣar teqqned?”
\v 9 Inna asen: “Necc d Aɛibrani uca ggʷedeɣ zi SIDI, AREBBI n ijenwan, wenni dd-ixeřqen řebḥar d řbar.”
\v 10 Iryazen \add nni\add* ggʷeden aṭṭas, nnan as: “Min teggid?” Minzi tuɣa ssnen, netta yarweř-dd zeg wudem n SIDI, aqa tuɣa zeɛma issxebbar i-ten.
\v 11 Uca nnan as: “Min zzayek i ɣa negg, ḥima ad xaneɣ ihedden řebḥar?” Minzi řebḥar tuɣa ɛad yarenni deg uhaji.
\v 12 Inna asen: “Ksim ayi u nḍarem ayi di řebḥar ḥima ad xawem ihedden řebḥar, minzi ssneɣ aqa taḥaryaḍt-a tameqqrant i xawem dd-iwḍan di ssibbet inu.”
\v 13 \add Maca\add* iryazen tuɣa qeddfen ɣar řbar, maca war d as zemmaren ca, minzi řebḥar tuɣa ɛad yarenni xasen aṭṭas s waṭṭas deg uhaji.
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* řaɣan i SIDI, nnan: “A SIDI, war d aneɣ ttejji ca ad nettwahellek di ssibbet n řeɛmar n weryaz-a uca war d aneɣ tḥessibed x idammen imezdagen, minzi Cek, a SIDI, teggid min d ac yarḍan.”
\v 15 \add Xas uca\add* ṭṭfen Yunus, nḍaren t di řebḥar. \add Řexdenni\add* ibedd uhaji n řebḥar.
\v 16 Ggʷden iryazen \add nni\add* aṭṭas zi SIDI uca ɣarṣen ict n tɣarṣt i SIDI uca waɛden lwuɛud.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Yunus deg wesřem
\m 
\v 1 Issewjed SIDI ijj n wesřem ameqqran ḥima ad isseɣri Yunus uca Yunus ikka třata n wussan d třata n ǧiyaři deg uɛeddis n wesřem. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Mt. 12:40; 16:4; Lk. 11:30\x*
\v 2 Uca iẓẓuǧ Yunus i SIDI, AREBBI nnes, zeg uɛeddis n wesřem.
\v 3 inna:
\b
\m \qt ”Zi řeḥṣaret inu řaɣiɣ i SIDI\qt*
\m \qt u Netta yarra-dd xafi.\qt*
\m \qt Zeg weḥwic n řaxart řaɣiɣ\qt*
\m \qt uca Cek tesřid i tmijja inu.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Izhd. 120:1\x*
\m 
\v 4 \qt Tuɣa tenḍared ayi di řaǧaɣ,\qt*
\m \qt deg wuř n řebḥur,\qt*
\m \qt tennḍen ayi-dd řemwaj.\qt*
\m \qt Marra zzhir nnec d řemwaj nnec\qt*
\m \qt kkin-dd xafi sennej.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt Izhd. 42:8\x*
\m 
\v 5 \qt Nniɣ: ‘Necc ttwassuffɣeɣ\qt*
\m \qt zi zzat i wudem nnec.\qt*
\m \qt Ɛad ad twařiɣ ɛawed\qt*
\m \qt Zzawect nnec Tameqqrant Iqeddsen.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Izhd. 31:23\x*
\m 
\v 6 \qt Ṭṭfen ayi waman\qt*
\m \qt ař mani iwḍen ɣar řeɛmar inu,\qt*
\m \qt \tl aman\tl* ihewřen nnḍen ayi-dd,\qt*
\m \qt iřṣeq-dd arbiɛ n řebḥar deg uzeǧif inu.\qt*
\m 
\v 7 \qt Hwiɣ ɣar ṭṭrufa yuǧɣen qaɛ n idurar,\qt*
\m \qt \tl ttwabellɛen\tl* zzekrunat n temmurt xafi\qt*
\m \qt sennej i řebda,\qt*
\m \qt maca Cek tessgeɛɛded tudart inu\qt*
\m \qt zi turṣuḍi \tl deg waman\tl*,\qt*
\m \qt \tl a\tl* SIDI, AREBBI inu!\qt*
\m 
\v 8 \qt Umi idewwex řeɛmar inu dayi,\qt*
\m \qt fekkareɣ di SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt u taẓaǧit inu tgeɛɛed ɣarek,\qt*
\m \qt di Zzawect nnec Tameqqrant Iqeddsen.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 2:8 \fk dayi\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘xafi’.\f*
\m 
\v 9 \qt Nitni ṭṭfen di \tl l’aṣnam\tl* ibeṭṭřen d iɣeccen,\qt*
\m \qt semḥen di tmexsiwt nsen icewwaren.\qt*
\m 
\v 10 \qt \tl Maca\tl* necc ad Cek ḥemdeɣ\qt*
\m \qt s yict n tmijja \tl teccur\tl* s uqadi.\qt*
\m \qt Min waɛdeɣ, ad \tl t\tl* qefřeɣ.\qt*
\m \qt Asenjem zi SIDI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Izhd. 3:9; 50:14, 23; 116:17; Ḥuc. 14:3; Ɛbr. 13:15\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 Issiweř SIDI ak-d wesřem uca iɛuqq-dd Yunus di řbar.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Ttubet n ayt n Ninwa
\m 
\v 1 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Yunus i twařa wiss tnayen, inna:
\v 2 “Kkar, ruḥ ɣar tendint n Ninwa tameqqrant uca barreḥ asen tabarreḥt nni i d ac ɣa iniɣ.”
\v 3 Uca ikkar Yunus, iruḥ ɣar Ninwa ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI. Tuɣa Ninwa d ict n tendint tameqqrant s waṭṭas, aqa \add ittxeṣṣa\add* ticři n třata n wussan \add i ucuqi\add*.
\v 4 Yudef Yunus tandint ticři n ijj n wass uca ibarreḥ, inna: “Awarni arebɛin n wussan ad tᵉttwaneqřeb \add tendint n\add* Ninwa.”
\v 5 Iryazen n Ninwa umnen di AREBBI uca barrḥen s yijj n uẓummi uca arḍen txuncay \add n wecḍan\add*, zeg umeqqran ař ameẓyan jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Mt. 12:41; Lk. 11:32\x*
\v 6 Yiweḍ wawař uřa ɣar ujeǧid n Ninwa uca ikkar zi řkursi n řɛarc nnes, ikkes xas arruḍ nnes igellden, issduriy ixef nnes s yict n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* uca iqqim x yiɣɣed.
\m 
\v 7 X řumur n ujeǧid \add jmiɛ ak-d\add* ayt n ccurfa ggin ad barrḥen di Ninwa, nnan: “War ttejjim bnadem d řmař d ifunasen d tfunasin d wuǧi ad ccen ca, war ten ttejjim ad hdan uřa ad swen. \f ◼ \fr 3:7 \fk ayt n ccurfa\ft - niɣ ‘ayt n taṣiřet’.\f*
\v 8 Jjem ad yarḍ bnadem d řmař tixuncay \add n wecḍan\add* uca jjem ten ad sɣuyen s jjehd ɣar AREBBI uca ad itub kuř ijj zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan u zi lɛunf \add i yumsen\add* ɣar ifassen nnes.
\v 9 Ad taɣ ad indem AREBBI uca ad itub uca ad ibeɛɛed x řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes ḥima war nettwathellik ca.” \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Yuw. 2:14\x*
\m 
\v 10 Uca iẓra AREBBI min ggin, aqa tuben x webrid nsen aɛeffan uca indem AREBBI x řɣar nni tuɣa inna ad kisen igg uca war t iggi ca.
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Iwebbex Arebbi i Yuna
\m 
\v 1 Man aya tuɣa d \add ict n tmesřact\add* taɛeffant ař ṭṭarf i Yunus uca thaj tefqeḥt nnes.
\v 2 Iẓẓuǧ i SIDI, inna: “\add A\add* SIDI, ma war nniɣ ammu umi d ayi tuɣa di temmurt inu? X uya nwiɣ ad tt jjeɣ umi ggiɣ ad arewřeɣ ɣar Tarcic minzi necc ssneɣ belli Cek d ijj n Arebbi d aḥnin d arḥim, ɣarek ttasiɛ n řxaḍar d tmexsiwt icewwaren tameqqrant uca tnedmed ad tegged řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt Uf. 34:6; Izhd. 86:5; Yuw. 2:13\x*
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* SIDI, kkes zzayi řeɛmar inu, minzi ittban ayi belli řmewt inu ḥsen zi tudart inu.”
\v 4 Inna SIDI: “Ma tecna umi txeyyqed ammu?”
\m 
\v 5 Iffeɣ Yunus zi tendint uca iruḥ iqqim di jjihet n ccarq n tendint mani igga i yixef nnes taseqqaft n ifetwan uca iqqim swadday nnes di tiři maḥend ad iẓar min ɣa imsaren i tendint.
\v 6 Tuɣa SIDI AREBBI issewjed ict n tcejjart n utebhet uca ijja-i-tt ad teyma tuɛřa x Yunus ḥima ad tiři d tiři x uzeǧif nnes u ḥima ad ikkes uxeyyeq nnes. Ifarḥ Yunus aṭṭas x tcejjart-a n řeɛjeb.
\v 7 Maca ɣar řefjar n twecca n wass i dd-iḍfaren issewjed AREBBI ict n tkecca nni tesseḥřec tacejjart n utebhet nni ařami tuẓeɣ.
\v 8 Ařami dd-tenqar tfuct, imsar belli AREBBI issekk ijj n usemmiḍ n ccarq iḥarren uca tewta tfuct azeǧif n Yunus ařami idewwex uca netta yarzu ad immet, inna: “Ittban ayi belli řmewt inu ḥsen zi tudart inu.”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna as AREBBI i Yunus: “Ma tecna umi txeyyqed ammu x tcejjart-a n utebhet?” Inna: “Aqa d ṣṣeḥ aqa xeyyqeɣ, ařami zemmareɣ ad mmteɣ!”
\v 10 Inna \add as\add* SIDI: “Cek tezziǧez ac tcejjart n utebhet i umi war txedmed u i umi war tesseymed, d tenni dd-yusin deg ict n ǧiřet uca tᵉttwahellek deg ict n ǧiřet.
\v 11 Ma Necc war d ayi tezziǧez tendint n Ninwa tameqqrant tenni i di iǧa ktar zi mya u-ɛicrin-ařef n iwdan inni war issinen \add řfarq\add* jar ufus nsen afusi d ufus nsen azeřmaḍ u sennej i uya \add aqa din\add* aṭṭas n řebhayem?” 
